{"tid":1293361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[跨國人口販賣?]美富豪淫媒艾普斯坦　涉販運未成年少女被捕","createTime":"2019-07-07T15:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T16:43:22.000Z","uid":145699,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"efc75fef5ba667659867b6b9f7a25ce4b5106e4b","tid":1293361,"uid":145699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190707/bkn-20190707152043028-0707_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190707%2Fbkn-20190707152043028-0707_00972_001.html&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=a5b1d066\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190707/bkn-20190707152043028-0707_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n元首級淫媒擁性圈子 傳多位名人涉事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20190226/robert-kraft-trafficking-florida/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fusa%2F20190226%2Frobert-kraft-trafficking-florida%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=d6b57a4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20190226/robert-kraft-trafficking-florida/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國破獲人口販賣及賣淫案，受害者來自中國，唔知有冇關係呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳聞Epstein接待政要嘅&quot;宮殿&quot;，唔知香港有冇人去過呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iip1eY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iip1eY.jpg&h=1fb9aa06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3DNezZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3DNezZ.jpg&h=baec26b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人想知多啲嘅話，可以搜尋Pizzagate，其實外國呢幾年已經有一班人track down咗係背後操縱嘅個體同組織，只不過一直冇實質証據，加上背後組織勢力龐大，所以一直冇人敢出面出力查，直到Trump落order叫DOJ去查，但啲主流媒體只係focus喺Trump同Epstein嘅關係度，黎抹黑Trump, 只係想政治謀殺Trump, 而Trump一早知Epstein有嘢,不過主流媒體(背後勢力龐大嘅組織)只係想政治謀殺Trump.<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/255294883680632833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F255294883680632833&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=760ec003\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F255294883680632833&h=3ed288a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/255294883680632833</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0vh0AklSXkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0vh0AklSXkU&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=7e20efd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0vh0AklSXkU</a><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.infowars.com/trump-doj-to-investigate-jeffrey-epstein-pedophile-deal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infowars.com%2Ftrump-doj-to-investigate-jeffrey-epstein-pedophile-deal%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=89b09c8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.infowars.com/trump-doj-to-investigate-jeffrey-epstein-pedophile-deal/</a><br />\n<br />\n正正係Trump叫DOJ查Epstein，不過主流媒體只係focus喺Trump同Epstein嘅關係<br />\n<br />\nTwitter上面件事已經炒到好熱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RitaPanahi/status/1147718700637667328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRitaPanahi%2Fstatus%2F1147718700637667328&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=f97f1a3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRitaPanahi%2Fstatus%2F1147718700637667328&h=4a03c954\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RitaPanahi/status/1147718700637667328</a><br />\n<br />\n件事牽涉各國政商名人，傳聞克林頓有份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/alexsalvinews/status/1147728721383571461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falexsalvinews%2Fstatus%2F1147728721383571461&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=690f6675\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Falexsalvinews%2Fstatus%2F1147728721383571461&h=b01f86eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/alexsalvinews/status/1147728721383571461</a><br />\n<br />\nThe judge who unsealed the #Epstein documents said the public&rsquo;s right to access case information outweighed the privacy of individuals, including:<br />\n&bull;Prominent American politicians<br />\n&bull;Powerful business executives<br />\n&bull;Foreign presidents<br />\n&bull;Prominent Prime Minister<br />\n&bull;Other world leaders <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DwXweiRjckI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDwXweiRjckI&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=03d2c380\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DwXweiRjckI</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知Biden有冇份呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903cf58ccec028d88befb46cf77dd3acd68e9290","tid":1293361,"uid":145699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"仲一年就大選，Trump開始要爆Dem大鑊"},{"pid":"005acbcf6c12cf140611a91aa21dea72bf70558d","tid":1293361,"uid":145699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:11:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JOktR-FbzvU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJOktR-FbzvU&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=7fed5990\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JOktR-FbzvU</a><br />\n22:50<br />\n2015年睇Trump點評論Epstein"},{"pid":"2906ef79ef65f19785af56e000f880d559a1325e","tid":1293361,"uid":83060,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"湯渣聽到好開心"},{"pid":"bf34b722813259ee5cc7199870ac6a4d9e7f6219","tid":1293361,"uid":145699